els. In addition,\nwe provide a methodology to reproduce our study for different models and\nsurveys, as well as discuss different options to handle eventual biases in the\nBAO measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Apr 2020 18:00:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Dec 2020 15:23:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-04"}
