opment of models for self-yielding of\nsoft active solids whose intrinsic active stresses fluidize or stiffen the\nnetwork.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Apr 2020 20:38:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 18 Apr 2020 17:02:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2020 15:51:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
