at most of the clouds are mixtures of these\ntwo types of clouds. Moreover, we suggest the following scenario of molecular\ngas formation: An HI-dominant cloud evolved with increasing H$_2$ mass along a\npath of $M_{{\\rm H}_2} \\propto M_{\\rm tot}^2$ by collecting diffuse gas before\nreaching and moving along the curves of the two sequences.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Apr 2020 10:53:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-17"}
