ift distribution of the X-ray sources. Contrary to the\noverall trend, the sources at the two higher-redshift spikes at z=1.61 and\nz=2.57 have puzzlingly low obscuration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Apr 2020 11:25:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 May 2020 13:58:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-08"}
